room_title: Escape room "The Runaway Train" by Quandary Escape Rooms in Sacramento
room_description: You are a team of mercenaries that have been hired to safeguard a shipment that is being sent from Dr. Clark, to Dr. Clements, to help cure a recent outbreak. Unfortunately, an escaped Mad Man from the events at the Dynaline Incident, has broken onto the train, and planted a bomb! Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to board the train, disarm the bomb, and get the explosives off. Will you save the equipment and prevent an outbreak, or go exploding off the rails?
